{"type": "article", "id": 24081, "title": "将动物拟人化的化妆品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060713372764cvw7nXgsiLAomx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这套化妆品来自韩国，包装上的插画来自汉城的插画师 Yeji Yun。他将各类动物拟人化，它们穿着人的衣服，做着人的活动，出现了游泳的兔子，看书的猫，骑自行车的大象，理发的狮子，煎蛋的鸡等种种有趣的生活场景，有个性而又有故事。使用动物的元素当然是为了体现出天然无害，在这些故事里又能引起你更多的联想。<a href=\"http://seeouterspace.com/studio/\">这里是工作链接</a>，他有很多类似有趣的插画。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133724G20WdL9KbgyPCjln.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133725E0ma1Uuk2fDbVCRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133725kdCbiNtrveyPDca6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607133726Ls3e1EhoWAZfBCOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}